title: Crash, missing injection, lifecycle fixes. Broken tests.
message:
Crash, missing injection, lifecycle fixes. Broken tests.

Current version works but does not handle activity restart correctly. Seems I forgot this is a thing. Ups.

Problem lays in the fact: old activity starts intent -> new activity receives -> old controller reacts. New activity has new controller injected.

More redesign is required in order to:
1. Either brink back old activity starts intent -> new activity receives -> new controller processes asynchronous mess
2. Make controllers great (for the first time) with correct view but otherwise have application (?) scope.
